# GameUp SDK Installer Flow

- Treat install and update as two explicit flows with clear completion checks.
- Before changing installer logic, verify package dependencies and define-symbol side effects.
- Keep startup behavior idempotent: avoid reopening setup UI repeatedly in one session.
- Use project-scoped persistence keys for setup completion and keep reset path available.
- When adding post-install steps, run them only after dependency checks succeed.
- For failures, keep logs actionable and include manual recovery instructions.
